{
  "title": "Peppery Silky Brazilian Lamb Kidney Stew",
  "description": "A hearty, nostalgic Brazilian dish featuring tender lamb kidney in a rich, peppery broth, slow-cooked to perfection. This gluten-free-friendly stew is sure to become a favorite.",
